outputs.output_descr:
The overall goal of the Joint Programme is to increase the number of women in China that can enjoy their right to a life free from domestic violence.  
The expected outcome of the program is the effective prevention and response to DV through implementing a multi-sectoral model and improving relevant policies and laws.

project_descr: Preventing and Responding to Domestic Violence in China
project_title: Preventing and Responding to Domestic Violence in China
